{"tid":2422920,"cid":22,"subCid":0,"title":"Apple iMac 2021 或推新色    銀、黑、綠、藍、粉紅共五款","createTime":"2021-02-25T14:16:39.000Z","updateTime":"2021-02-26T06:29:39.000Z","uid":66271,"like":0,"dislike":10,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"e14159c228a485962282ebb882d53df65697b3b7","tid":2422920,"uid":66271,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-25T14:16:39.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/EvALc0wU4AMtOXj-624x351-1.jpeg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.unwire.hk%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2021%2F02%2FEvALc0wU4AMtOXj-624x351-1.jpeg&h=62f9b75c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n當提到 iMac 顏色，大家腦海浮現的就僅僅有銀色。不像 iPhone 和 iPad 有多種顏色選擇。不<br />\n<br />\n知名爆料達人 Jon Prosser ，早前於 Twitter 中發怖了 iMac 多色版本的爆料圖 (共 5 色)，更直接寫出「Hello, 1998. iMacs. Colors. They &lsquo;re back.」。同時 Jon Prosser 發怖了一條詳細的 YouTube 影片，部分內容與上月 Bloomberg 出版的報導一致。影片提到， iMac 2021 將採用窄邊框熒幕設計，外觀與 Apple Pro Display XDR 熒幕類似，又看起來像是放大版的 iPad。另外，iMac 2021 可能會搭載新一代的 Apple Silicon 處理器，擁有高達 16 核心。"},{"pid":"aa7de1305641e2ccd885fd9acc7e5f26cd2e51a6","tid":2422920,"uid":27946,"like":14,"dislike":0,"score":14,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-02-25T15:47:42.000Z","msg":"個設計好唔掂<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"164944d99d77d4460a64b41c5b3e98b7694090a0","tid":2422920,"uid":32906,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"quote":{"pid":"aa7de1305641e2ccd885fd9acc7e5f26cd2e51a6","tid":2422920,"uid":27946,"like":14,"dislike":0,"score":14,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-02-25T15:47:42.000Z","msg":"個設計好唔掂<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-25T16:25:57.000Z","msg":"但好過舊果d"},{"pid":"8ff1e245a0e8a02981bbc7972028b0618bc511f6","tid":2422920,"uid":95096,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"aa7de1305641e2ccd885fd9acc7e5f26cd2e51a6","tid":2422920,"uid":27946,"like":14,"dislike":0,"score":14,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-02-25T15:47:42.000Z","msg":"個設計好唔掂<img s